    <article class="value-item">
      <h2>User-Centered Design</h2>
      <p>
        Every design decision should be made with the user in mind. I believe in understanding 
        user needs through research, testing, and empathy to create solutions that truly serve people.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="value-item">
      <h2>Simplicity</h2>
      <p>
        The best designs are often the simplest. I strive to remove complexity and create 
        intuitive experiences that don't require explanation.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="value-item">
      <h2>Accessibility</h2>
      <p>
        Good design is inclusive design. I believe in creating experiences that work for everyone, 
        regardless of ability, device, or context.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="value-item">
      <h2>Continuous Learning</h2>
      <p>
        The field of design and technology is constantly evolving. I'm committed to staying 
        curious, learning new skills, and adapting to change.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="value-item">
      <h2>Collaboration</h2>
      <p>
        The best products come from diverse teams working together. I value open communication, 
        constructive feedback, and building on each other's ideas.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
